# UINavigationItem.ItemStyle.navigator

**Case**

A style for a traditional navigation-based interface.

## Declaration

```swift
case navigator
```

## Discussion

Use this style for apps that support a traditional hierarchical navigation model. With this style, the navigation item’s title appears in the center of the navigation bar, and center items ([doc://com.apple.uikit/documentation/UIKit/UINavigationItem/centerItemGroups]) appear in the overflow menu.

## Constants

- **UINavigationItem.ItemStyle.browser**: A style for a browser app interface.
- **UINavigationItem.ItemStyle.editor**: A style for an editor app interface.
